title: Housing Society
description:
Housing Society is a web platform where a user can book resources from a society such as hall, garden, etc.
It is made wih React js Node js and MySQL.

title: Cryptos
description:
Cryptos is a web platform where a user can see the current price and the last 24hr rate change in crypto value.
It is made using React js and api from coingecko.

title: Expense Tracker
description:
Expense Tracker is a web patform where user can monitor their day to day expenses and can keep record of it.
It is made with React JS.
